These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Music-Genre: metal, jazz, blues, punk
1. Music-Genre:punk is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Music-Genre:jazz##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:blues is on the left or right of Music-Genre:punk##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Music-Genre        | metal | jazz   | punk | blues    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Sport: surfing, skiing, sailing, snowboarding
Nationality: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. Sport:skiing is on the left of Sport:snowboarding##1
2. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:french == Sport:surfing##1
5. Nationality:german is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
6. Nationality:french == Sport:surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | sailing | surfing  | skiing  | snowboarding |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
Job: nurse, firefighter, librarian, writer
1. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of Job:writer##3
2. Food:pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. Job:writer is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3
4. Job:writer is on the right of Job:librarian##1
5. Job:nurse is in an odd position##4
6. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Job   | librarian        | writer     | nurse | firefighter |

