.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Pet: bird, horse, guinea-pig, hamster
Music-Genre: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. Pet:horse is between Music-Genre:blues and Music-Genre:reggae##2
2. Pet:hamster is on the left of Pet:bird##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Music-Genre:reggae##1
5. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Pet:bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet         | hamster | bird | horse | guinea-pig |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

