5. Job:coach is between Job:teacher and Job:pilot##2
6. Movie-Genre:action is in an odd position##4
7. Movie-Genre:action is between Job:coach and Movie-Genre:adventure##2
8. Job:coach is on the left or right of Job:pilot##3

