2. Nationality:french is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Nationality:indonesian is between Nationality:french and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Nationality:indonesian is on the left or right of Nationality:french##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Nationality:russian##3

