.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: 7up, fanta, milk, water
Nationality: dutch, american, turkish, german
1. Nationality:american is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
3. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
4. Nationality:turkish is on the left of Nationality:german##1
5. Nationality:german is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. Nationality:turkish is in an even position##4
7. Nationality:dutch == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Nationality       | american  | turkish | german | dutch  |

